A subscriber can register for multiple entries in routing table ,
in this eg: T1 can register for any number of entries in routing table

A subscriber can subscribe/unsubscribe at his will
in this eg:
Publisher thread owns data table and rest of subscriber threads maybe interested any of table entry's
there could be any number of subscribers and they can subscribe for any entry in the Routing table
it means that, each entry is associated with its own Notification chains(linkedlist of subscribers)
